Jab.help: You strike your target with a quick jab. This causes smashing damage and has a small chance to stun the target.
Jab.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG (Smashing), Chance for Stun (Foe)

Punch.help: You strike your target with a strong punch. This causes smashing damage and has the potential to knock the target back.
Punch.shortHelp: Melee, High DMG (Smashing), Chance for Knockback (Foe)

Foot_Stomp.help: Using your superior leg strength, you can stomp your foot to the ground, quaking the earth itself. Any targets around you affected by this attack suffer smashing damage and may be knocked down.
Foot_Stomp.shortHelp: PBAoE, High DMG (Smashing), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)

Dull_Pain.help: Using your superior metabolism, you can make yourself more resilient to pain, allowing you to suffer more damage before being defeated. When you activate this power you will increase your maximum Hit Points for a couple of minutes.
Dull_Pain.attackerHit: Your {PowerName} has increased your maximum Hit Points.

Metabolic_Superiority.help: Your superior metabolism increases your base regeneration rate. This is so powerful an effect that there is a small chance that it will occasionally heal you outright.

Integration.help: You can integrate your mind and body, making you resistant to Knockback, Disorient, Hold, Sleep, and Immobilization effects. This also increases your regeneration rate, but the effect is suppressed if you are affected by controls like Hold, Sleep or Stun.
Integration.attackerHit: You are now highly resistant to Disorient, Immobilize, Hold, Sleep and Knockback.
